{"tid":947971,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"海關打擊健身中心不良營商手法拘四人","createTime":"2018-12-19T16:21:22.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T17:02:05.000Z","uid":52824,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"32d4e1f5a9c03c08c36ed4e8ecc239f0bd9f2974","tid":947971,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:21:22.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】海關調查一間健身中心於旺角及油麻地兩間分店拘捕四名職員，涉嫌以不良營商手法銷售服務。  <br />\n被捕四名健身中心男職員年齡21至23歲，涉嫌違反商品說明條例被押上車帶走調查。海關早前接獲舉報，指有健身中心職員涉嫌使用具威嚇性營業行為銷售健身服務，涉及四名受害人，金額超過30萬元。<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=331345&amp;refer=Share\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331345%26refer%3DShare&d=CplsXHUpDta2qU6L8%2Fp1%2FXIou9iuErJt32EjuWI86Zw%3D&h=a12865b7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D331345%26refer%3DShare&h=d1e854df\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=331345&amp;refer=Share</a><br />\n<br />\n有無巴打知邊間<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868889b0b6f91e09850c8894175718240f2f887e","tid":947971,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"九成九都係p記啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44f7ce1a1dfdae70ede9dfc5016194b55d243a84","tid":947971,"uid":52824,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"868889b0b6f91e09850c8894175718240f2f887e","tid":947971,"uid":165336,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T16:25:43.000Z","msg":"九成九都係p記啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T17:02:05.000Z","msg":"油麻地無分店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}